    SlideLeftFadeOut
    SlideRightFadeIn
    SlideRightFadeOut
    SlideUpFadeIn
    SlideUpFadeOut
    
    ###SwivelTransitionMode###
    BackwardIn
    BackwardOut
    ForwardIn
    ForwardOut
    FullScreenIn
    FullScreenOut
    
    ###TurnstileTransition###
    BackwardIn
